  1. \`bun run check\`  (tsc --noEmit)
  2. \`bun run lint\`   (biome check src)
  3. \`bun test\`       (whole suite must stay green — do not break existing tests)
  4. \`grep -rn "minima_db\\|bun:sqlite\\|MinimaDb" src/minima/plan_session.ts src/minima/plan_council.ts tests/plan_session.test.ts tests/plan_council.test.ts\`  (MUST return nothing — the feature is DB-free)
